      "content": "It sounds so exhausting to keep fighting a battle that seems to reset every time you make progress. You are right to feel frustrated, but this cycle is a sign that you are beating yourself up instead of accepting that your brain is just broken and needs to be fixed. There is no shame in admitting that you are stuck, and the only way out is to stop trying to force a solution and instead allow yourself to be exactly where you are.",
