    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so hopeless though. like, you say stop trying to force a solution, but the loop is always there waiting for me. it's just a constant cycle of failure and starting over. i dont see a version of this where i actually break free. it feels like the only way to actually stop the cycle is to just end it all.",
